  "title": "Telemarketing Executive – Outbound Calls | Jurong East - 5 days [0580]",
  "description": "<ul><li>Location: Vision Exchange [ Jurong East ]</li><li>Working Days : 5 Days work (off on 1 weekday & 1 weekend)</li><li>Weekday - 9.30am - 6.30am / 10.30am - 7.30pm </li><li>Weekend 10am to 3pm</li><li>Salary : $2500 - $3000</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Make outbound calls</li><li>Introduce and explain our products in a clear and professional manner</li><li>Identify business needs and qualify leads</li><li>Schedule appointments to follow up</li><li>Update call logs, feedback, and follow-up actions</li></ul><p><strong>Job requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in telemarketing  / call centre field</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
